# Copy this to /etc/dip-alert/deploy-alert.env on the VM (root:root, chmod 600).
# Loaded ONLY by dip-alert-deploy.service — deliberately separate from
# dip-alert.env so the internet-facing app process never carries these creds.
# Optional: leave blank to disable deploy-failure alerts.
#
# These are the DEVELOPER's OWN CallMeBot phone + key (where deploy failures are
# sent) — NOT the friend's app-alert creds (those live in the app's DB). Get a
# key via the one-time CallMeBot handshake described in the main README.md.
DEPLOY_ALERT_PHONE=
DEPLOY_ALERT_APIKEY=
